Then we define the size, height, and fringe of the tree:

```tactics
def Tree.size {α : Type} : Tree α → Nat
 | Tree.leaf _ => 1
 | Tree.node t₁ t₂ => t₁.size + t₂.size

def Tree.height {α : Type} : Tree α → Nat
 | Tree.leaf _ => 0
 | Tree.node t₁ t₂ => Nat.max t₁.height t₂.height + 1

