`= spine (List.foldl (fun u v => .node u v) (Tree.leaf x) ts) ++ [t]`
By the induction hypothesis, this is `([Tree.leaf x] ++ ts) ++ [t]`
`= [Tree.leaf x] ++ (ts ++ [t])`
`= [Tree.leaf x] ++ (t :: ts)`

